title: Anne's House of Dreams
creator: Lucy Maud Montgomery
description: LibriVox recording of Anne's house of Dreams, by Lucy Maud Montgomery. Anne's House of Dreams is book five in the series, and chronicles Anne's early married life, as she and her childhood sweetheart Gilbert Blythe begin to build their life together. (Summary from Wikipedia) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
